        "label": "The Problem",
        "headline": "Tired of the Breakout-Congestion Cycle?",
        "body": "<p>Managing acne-prone skin can feel like a frustrating battle. Many treatments strip skin, making breakouts worse.</p><p><strong>A Damaged Barrier Leads to More Breakouts.</strong> Over-stripping weakens the skin\u2019s defence system.</p><p><strong>An Unbalanced Microbiome Fuels Acne.</strong> Disrupted bacteria leads to persistent pimples.</p><p><strong>Congestion is the Starting Point.</strong> Clogged pores create the perfect environment for acne.</p>",
        "bg": "muted",
        "width": "narrow"
      }
    },
